Class BasePropertyComponent

java.lang.Object
javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.TagSupport
javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.BodyTagSupport
br.com.concepting.framework.ui.components.BaseComponent
br.com.concepting.framework.ui.components.BaseActionFormComponent

All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.BodyTag, javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.IterationTag, javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.JspTag, javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.Tag
Direct Known Subclasses:
BaseOptionPropertyComponent, BaseOptionsPropertyComponent, ColorPickerPropertyComponent, DownloadPropertyComponent, HiddenPropertyComponent, ImageComponent, LabelComponent, MapsComponent, ProgressBarComponent, RichTextAreaPropertyComponent, TextPropertyComponent
public abstract class BasePropertyComponent extends BaseActionFormComponent
Class that defines the basic implementation for the component that refers to a property of a data model.
